{"tid":994692,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"依家邊度仲有好食既豉油王炒麵？","createTime":"2019-01-25T01:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T18:58:27.000Z","uid":11097,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"73647b585656afbb3cd81067918b3b3d64941592","tid":994692,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T01:33:23.000Z","msg":"細細個食果種豉油王炒麵係好乾身<br />\n麵身係幻既，食落口唔會一啖油，條條麵身分明，甜甜地，再西利啲既會有埋鑊氣。蔥唔會太生唔會太熟，咬落去係爽口既，配埋辣椒醬真係可以連食三碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味依家食果堆垃圾，食落去一堆油，一D都唔爽口<br />\n麵又煮到淋撚曬先落鑊炒，最撚慘係啲豉油，屌你老味好似冇落到咁一啲味都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n請問各區巴絲有冇好既豉油王炒麵推介？唔想再侮辱自己兒時回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e73c405c26755403c5abd28abd15c28d45dd147","tid":994692,"uid":128928,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T01:38:20.000Z","msg":"乜麵身可以幻架？"},{"pid":"8eba07e3e655beeb7dc833541cdbfd6716b6728d","tid":994692,"uid":153615,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T01:39:18.000Z","msg":"迷幻麵？"},{"pid":"7e73c03572e87723ac00ae210cb50c0548ce4388","tid":994692,"uid":165735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eba07e3e655beeb7dc833541cdbfd6716b6728d","tid":994692,"uid":153615,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T01:39:18.000Z","msg":"迷幻麵？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T01:40:30.000Z","msg":"999"},{"pid":"3513592a26bf510a6443a1dbf27d7f14df16ddb2","tid":994692,"uid":191443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T01:41:08.000Z","msg":"加杯凍幻茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4a2dc14f96bb29980a9ccf556e0f031a00befe","tid":994692,"uid":11097,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T01:46:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幼，自膠</span></span>"},{"pid":"1b1e7e1113fcc3851620d8